= SDL_GetKeyboardFocus =
Use this function to get the window which currently has keyboard focus.


== Syntax ==
<syntaxhighlight lang='c++'>
SDL_Window* SDL_GetKeyboardFocus(void)
</syntaxhighlight>

== Return Value ==
Returns the window with keyboard focus.

